      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks. What about the other side, though? There are a lot of people in the industry saying that heavy regulation will just kill innovation and let other countries get ahead. Is there any evidence that these existential risks are actually likely, or is it mostly just speculation?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
